sources.description:
*Monster Island* - As the world tries to stop a giant Kaiju bent on destruction more and more monsters appear - each one more terrible than the last - leaving mankind defenseless until our heroes reach out to a specialist versed in monster lore.
2019.  Stars: Eric Roberts, Toshi Toda, Adrian Bouchet

*King Of The Lost World* - Sir Arthur Conan Doyle's action-adventure classic, four plane crash survivors encounter danger in a world that time forgot.
2004.  Stars: Bruce Boxleitner, Jeff Denton, Rhett Giles
